        <source>getRawVoyageCode() : String;

/*
Purpose:	Return the appropriate rawVoyageCode to be used in the EDIConfig allEDITrackedItemsByVoyageCode collection.

Date			Who		Reason
11 June 2010	cnwrl1	Initial creation as part of PAR 24299 - SFW 1118 EDI Form to allow searching of EDI file by Container / Voyage
